            //INTRODUCTION TO LangChain (User side)

//WHAT is LangChain?
LangChain is an open source framnework that helps in building LLM based applications.
It provides modular components and end-to-end tools that help developers build complex AI 
applications, such as chatbots, question-answering systems, retrieval- augmented generation(RAG), autonomous agents, and more.

1. Supports all the major LLMs
2.Simplifies developing LLM based applications
3.Integration available for all major tools
4.Open source/free/actively developed.
5.Supports all major GenAI use cases.


